review.title: dreadful cheap sandpaper
review.author: A Tesco Customer
review.text: These tissues are like sandpaper, they never were as bad as the last box i recently bought, if this is what Tesco call luxury soft tissues , then there has to be a mistake or something wrong in the manufacturing.
